              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma rays were detected by a total",
                "absorption spectrometer HECTOR, consisting of 16",
                "NaI(Tl) segments, each read by two photomultiplier",
                "tubes. The array covered nearly the 4Pi solid angle.",
                "Targets were placed in the centre of the array."
              ]
            }
          ],
